extends layouts/main

block content
  .container(style="padding: 4rem 2rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;")
    h1(style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-900); margin-bottom: 2rem;") Terms of Service
    p(style="color: var(--gray-500); margin-bottom: 2rem;") Last updated: December 2025
    
    .policy-content(style="line-height: 1.8; color: var(--gray-700);")
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 1. Acceptance of Terms
      p By accessing and using EaseTrip, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws and regulations. If you do not agree with any of these terms, you are prohibited from using this platform.
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 2. User Accounts
      p To use certain features of EaseTrip, you must create an account. You are responsible for:
      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2rem;")
        li Maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials
        li All activities that occur under your account
        li Providing accurate and complete information
        li Notifying us immediately of any unauthorized use
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 3. Booking and Cancellation
      p When you make a booking through EaseTrip:
      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2rem;")
        li You agree to pay the total amount shown at checkout
        li Cancellation policies vary by listing and are displayed before booking
        li Hosts may have specific rules that you must follow
        li EaseTrip acts as an intermediary and is not a party to the rental agreement
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 4. Host Responsibilities
      p If you list a property on EaseTrip, you agree to:
      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2rem;")
        li Provide accurate and complete listing information
        li Maintain the property as described in your listing
        li Comply with all local laws and regulations
        li Respond to booking requests in a timely manner
        li Honor confirmed reservations
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 5. Prohibited Activities
      p You may not use EaseTrip to:
      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2rem;")
        li Violate any laws or regulations
        li Post false, misleading, or fraudulent content
        li Harass, abuse, or discriminate against others
        li Attempt to circumvent our fee structure
        li Upload malicious software or content
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 6. Payment Terms
      p All payments are processed securely through our payment partners:
      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2rem;")
        li Guests pay the full amount at the time of booking
        li EaseTrip charges a service fee for platform use
        li Hosts receive payouts after guest check-in
        li Refunds are subject to the cancellation policy
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 7. Limitation of Liability
      p EaseTrip is not liable for:
      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2rem;")
        li Actions or omissions of hosts or guests
        li Property damage or personal injury
        li Loss or theft of personal belongings
        li Service interruptions or technical issues
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 8. Dispute Resolution
      p In case of disputes between hosts and guests, EaseTrip may mediate at our discretion. For unresolved issues, disputes shall be settled through arbitration in Malaysia in accordance with Malaysian law.
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 9. Changes to Terms
      p We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of EaseTrip after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 10. Contact Us
      p If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
      p(style="margin-top: 1rem;")
        strong Email: 
        | legal@easetrip.my
      p
        strong Address: 
        | EaseTrip Sdn Bhd, Level 10, Menara KLCC, Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia
